{"type":"message","id":"376107b3","parentId":"1028073a","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:22:25.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 好的，查询结果返回了。历史数据相关的折线图功能主要在 HistoryCharts.vue 和 TaskDetails 相关文件中。\n\n从匹配结果来看：\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskDetails/HistoryCharts.vue` - 这是历史折线图组件\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskDetails/index.vue` - 这是任务详情面板\n\n关键函数：\n- selectChartsFn - 图表选择函数\n- setChartsNewOptions - 设置图表新选项\n- changeSensorUnit - 改变传感器单位\n\n看起来这是一个ECharts图表组件，用户想给折线图点击加效果。\n\n我应该按照指定的三段格式回复：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" 还在的 👋\n\n【建议】 历史折线图交互效果主要修改 `HistoryCharts.vue`。图表点击效果可在 `selectChartsFn` 函数内添加 ECharts 点击事件监听，结合 `handleClickOutside` 处理弹窗或高亮效果。如需自定义点样式，检查 `setChartsNewOptions` 中的图表配置，添加 `emphasis` 或 `itemStyle` 配置。\n\n【相关模块】\n- TaskDetails - 任务详情模块（包含历史图表）\n- HistoryCloud - 历史云图主模块\n- Realtime - Realtime/AutoWork（含面板交互参考）\n\n【涉及文件】\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskDetails/HistoryCharts.vue` (symbols: selectChartsFn, setChartsNewOptions, changeSensorUnit) - 折线图核心组件\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskDetails/index.vue` (symbols: handleClickOutside, assignPopoverPosition) - 点击外部处理、弹窗定位\n- `src/views/Realtime/components/AutoWork/index.vue` (symbols: handleDraw, handleTrackHover, handlePreviewCircle) - hover/预览交互参考\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskList.vue` (symbols: changeLayerHeight, renderLayer) - 列表层切换参考"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":14895,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15307,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776021738596,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a7ca1f7104f315a2"}}
